---
title: Hot Honey Hot Dog and French Fries with Ranch Drizzle and Rocket Salad
description: An American favourite but with a twist, this Hot Honey Hot Dog and French Fries combines hot sauce with sweet honey for a deliciously simple glaze. Creamy ranch dressing is there to cool it down though!
